LingerieCart
============

# Installation
1. composer and Magento
2. store credentials for repo.magento.com in /Users/Damon/.composer/auth.json
3. use xampp php: (http://andyy.me/mcrypt-php-extension-for-laravel-in-xampp-mac/)
   $ sudo nano ~/.bash_profile
   add "export PATH="/Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/bin:$PATH""
4. !!!: solve the problem when install Magento!!! IMPORTANT
   http://mrgott.com/misc/10-install-mcrypt-and-intl-php-extensions-on-mac-os-x-and-xampp
5. File system permission
   Enable xamp rewrite module
   http://www.leonardaustin.com/blog/technical/enable-mod_rewrite-in-xampp/
6. Install sample data: and remember to
   $ php <your Magento install dir>/bin/magento setup:upgrade
6. static files: php -dmemory_limit=6G bin/magento setup:static-content:deploy
